Oil (Oleum), Volatile / Not Fixed / Active, Fixed (Fixum), Dead Head / Residue (Caput Mortuum), Ammonia (Ammoniatum), Potassium Sulfate (Salpo), Borax (Sodium Biborate), Crystals (Crystalli), Dust (Pulvis).

